---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Axsetra KB | Secure Financial Software & Privacy Infrastructure"
  description="Secure financial software and privacy-focused infrastructure. Software development and technical consulting. Licensed in the Republic of Kiribati."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">Axsetra KB</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">Axsetra KB</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/images/logo.webp" alt="Logo" class="hero-logo" width="200" height="auto" />
    <h1>Axsetra KB</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Personal · Security · Finance · Digital Assets</p>
    <p>Secure financial software and privacy-focused infrastructure</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Secure Web Platforms</h2>
      <p>Multilingual websites with Python integrations for complex business needs.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Internet Banking Software (AXSE)</h2>
      <p>Production-ready banking solution covering accounts, payments, and compliance.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>VPS Hardening & Infrastructure</h2>
      <p>Isolation, encryption, and access control systems.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Dedicated Private VPN</h2>
      <p>No-logs service with custom exit country; not shared among clients.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Token & Exchange Development</h2>
      <p>Token creation on ETH, BNB Chain, Solana. DEX/CEX systems with integrated wallets and trading functionality.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Privacy Domain Setup</h2>
      <p>Web identity configuration with jurisdiction awareness.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <section class="registration-info">
    <h2>Registration & Legal</h2>
    <p><strong>License:</strong> KBN-40-000001 (Business/Commercial)</p>
    <p><strong>Authority:</strong> Kiribati International Financial Authority (KIFA)</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> axsetrakb@proton.me</p>
  </section>

  <section class="disclaimer">
    <p>Axsetra KB provides software development and technical consulting only. No financial services, brokerage, custody, or public exchange operations are offered.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-logo {
    max-width: 200px;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .registration-info {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .registration-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }
  .registration-info p {
    margin: 6px 0;
    color: #555;
  }
  .disclaimer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
